          "VALUES": [
            "<LOCATION>",
            "Alibaba offers delivery services because of the goal of convenience. We do not encourage our customers to come to our office since products can be brought to their door steps.",
            "Our standard delivery timeline is 4-9 days. As soon as your order is dispatched from our warehouse, you will receive an email to confirm that your package is on its way. You will also be contacted by our dispatch personnel on the day of delivery.",
            "Unfortunately, once you\u2019ve placed your order, it is not possible to amend any details, as our warehouse team will have already started processing your order.",
            "To make sure you receive your items as fast as possible, we start processing your order as soon as we receive it. This means that once your order has been placed, you will be unable to cancel it.",
            "We hope you\u2019ll love every Shopozine purchase you make. But if you ever need to return an item, you can do so within 7 days of receipt.",
            "Our ordering system will automatically send you an email confirming that your order was successfully submitted. Please make certain that the email address you provide is correct. Generated e-mail will contain all the details related to your order and shipping order number for your records.",
